title: The O'Neill Cold Water Classic Tour featuring Mishka Kicks Off on October 14th
description: The O'Neill Cold Water Classic Series is in the home stretch with the final two stops set for Tofino, BC and Santa Cruz, CA. To celebrate these last stops, O'Neill is supporting a West Coast tour by j.k. livin artist Mishka, who will follow the Series from Canada to the Western U.S....and starting today, tickets are available for all shows! Click on the Cold Water Classic Tour banner on the homepage for tour details.
